    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "「ワイは奥山すみれちゃうでぇ！」とか妙な関西弁\n使ってましたけど……それにしたって鉄壁過ぎますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "「ワイは奥山すみれちゃうでぇ！」とか妙な関西弁\n使ってましたけど……それにしたって鉄壁過ぎますよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.4144898196
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルの行動に目を光らせるのも\nマネージャーとしての仕事の内だからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "アイドルの行動に目を光らせるのも\nマネージャーとしての仕事の内だからな",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "どこにいようとも見逃すことはないよ\n例えそこが満員のドーム会場であろうともな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "どこにいようとも見逃すことはないよ\n例えそこが満員のドーム会場であろうともな",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.947823153
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、{user}さん\n私達のわがままで迷惑を掛けちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ごめんなさい、{user}さん\n私達のわがままで迷惑を掛けちゃって……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……いや、謝るのは俺の方だ\nみんなへの気遣いが足りていなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……いや、謝るのは俺の方だ\nみんなへの気遣いが足りていなかった",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.181156232
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
