      "text": "せっかくの大阪だし、もっと楽しみたいよな\n観光も休憩の内ではあるだろうし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "せっかくの大阪だし、もっと楽しみたいよな\n観光も休憩の内ではあるだろうし……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.581156232
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "お？　つまりつまり？\nはっきり言ってくれないと分かりませんよ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "お？　つまりつまり？\nはっきり言ってくれないと分かりませんよ～？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "こころはもう少し反省しような。まだ時間はあるし\nせっかくだから今からみんなで繁華街に出掛けようか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "こころはもう少し反省しような。まだ時間はあるし\nせっかくだから今からみんなで繁華街に出掛けようか",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2000020344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.2000020344
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "やりたいことをやりきって、すっきりした状態で\n明日のライブに臨もうじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "やりたいことをやりきって、すっきりした状態で\n明日のライブに臨もうじゃないか",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
